<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy" %>
<% content_for :meta_description, "Privacy policy for MRDBID, including data collection, cookies, analytics, and advertising disclosures." %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Last updated: April 14, 2026</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    MRDBID may collect account information you provide (such as email and display name), content you submit
    (such as specimen notes, images, and article text), and basic technical information needed to operate the site.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">2. How Information Is Used</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    Information is used to provide site functionality, maintain accounts, improve features, and support the
    documentation and educational goals of the project.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. Cookies, Analytics, and Advertising</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    MRDBID may use cookies and similar technologies for site operation, analytics, and advertising.
    When Google AdSense ads are shown, Google and its partners may use cookies to serve and personalize ads.
  </p>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    Learn more about how Google uses information:
    <a class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      How Google uses information from sites or apps that use its services
    </a>.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    MRDBID does not sell personal information. Data may be shared with service providers required to run the site
    (for example hosting, infrastructure, or email delivery).
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">5. Data Retention and Security</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    Reasonable technical and administrative steps are used to protect site data. No internet service can guarantee
    absolute security.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">6. Your Choices</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    You can contact us about account or privacy questions through the
    <%= link_to "Contact page", contact_path, class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline" %>.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">7. Policy Updates</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700">
    This policy may be updated from time to time. Material changes will be reflected by updating the date at the top
    of this page.
  </p>
</div>
